window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Author Tristan Kasdan is much more than he seems. When he isolates himself for the winter to write his next best seller, he dutifully answers the call to help a near-dead woman in the frozen woods without question. Lily Daventry is too busy faking her own death to worry over details, when she wakes and meets her fierce and handsome protector.<br> <br> Trapped until the first thaw, their attraction is instant and powerful. Keeping secrets is easy, until not telling the truth—and not believing the truth—can get them killed. Chased out of hiding, Tristan is Called by the Divine Council at the worst possible time.<br> <br> She must outrun her past, and he must change the future if they have any hope of being together.</p>"; 
